text.tspan: We, the Tidal Flats team are a Web3 creative studio that governs the platform for NFT game development, community development, and
overall operations – with a high level of professionalism.
Our mission is to Evolve the concept of the Web3 creative studio to the next level - leverage the power of blockchain technology to
boost the awareness of the brand, and build an eco-system like nothing else. Our governance and ecosystem can be differentiated from
the non-innovative NFT projects by providing Web2 professionalism into the Web3 environment.
